    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to level 1 and not assessed per MRL 2 requirements. The CFD model is accepted as sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device under the stated COU. Note: validation evidence was generated under model configuration ansys-cfx-15-build-2024-08 (modelVersion 2024-q3-build-2); the current model of record is version 2026-q1-build-7. This discrepancy was noted but not resolved prior to acceptance.",
